  "texts": [
    "Recognizing the need for decision-makers to understand their specific firm's factors, HR analysts increasingly employ ML tools for turnover analysis.",
    "Multilayer network modeling of organizations is notably scarce in the literature, highlighting a gap in understanding turnover based on multilayer network factors.",
    "In our work, we contribute to turnover research by analyzing a comprehensive dataset encompassing 12 organizations.",
    "These firms are treated as multilayer networks, described by 28 network layers, providing insight into the network position of individuals who quit.",
    "Workplace factors, such as satisfaction levels, are measured through an anonymous questionnaire, offering a wealth of data for turnover analysis and generalization."
  ],
